task.name: Login
task.documentation: The user inputs the login info.

task.name: Credentials Checked
task.documentation: The credentials are sent to the system and checked and in the next step the results are shown.

task.name: Select Product
task.documentation: The user chooses the product he wants.

task.name: Credentials Unavailable
task.documentation: If the credentials are not found the process is finished. The user has to restart the process

task.name: Add To Shopcart
task.documentation: The user adds the product to the cart.

task.name: Save Product
task.documentation: The user saves the product for later checkout

task.name: Check Product
task.documentation: The user checks if all products are in the cart.

task.name: Finalize Order
task.documentation: The order is being finalized by the system.

task.name: Payment Prepared
task.documentation: The payment is prepared depending on the region and payment options for it.

task.name: Prepare Shipment
task.documentation: The system prepares the shipping info depending on the customer location and the products.

task.name: Add Products
task.documentation: The user goes back to add additional products.

task.name: Enter Payment Data
task.documentation: The user enters his payment data.

task.name: Enter Shipping Address
task.documentation: The user enters his/her shipping address.

task.name: Processing Payment
task.documentation: The payment is processed and info received by the bank

task.name: Enter Billing Address
task.documentation: The user enters the billing address.

task.name: Confirm Choice
task.documentation: The user confirms the shipping and billing address are the same.

exclusiveGateway.name: Shipping Address equal to Billing Address?

task.name: Receive Order Confirmation
task.documentation: The user receives the order confirmation from the system that was generated.
